# Food Delivery App – UI/UX Design Project

## Abstract
This project focuses on designing a mobile food delivery application with a strong emphasis on simplicity, usability, and visual hierarchy. The goal is to provide users with a seamless experience for browsing food, placing orders, and completing checkout efficiently.

## Problem Statement
Many existing food delivery applications have cluttered interfaces and complex navigation, which negatively affect user experience and increase order abandonment.

## Proposed Solution
A clean, minimal, and user-friendly UI was designed with intuitive navigation, categorized menus, and a simplified checkout process.

## Target Users
- Students
- Working professionals
- Families

## User Flow
Home → Browse Categories → Select Restaurant → View Menu → Add to Cart → Checkout → Order Confirmation

## Key Screens
- Home Screen
- Menu Screen
- Checkout Screen

